🔢 Total Attributes Count:-
👉 Direct top-level <entry> count karte hain:-
✔️ Simple entries:-
Domain Admins
Enterprise Admins
Account Operators

✔️ Complex (nested Map) entries:-
VPN_External_Access
AWS_Production_ReadWrite

✅ Final Answer:-
👉 Total attributes (top-level entries) = 5

🔥 Total including inner?
👉 Agar sab count kare:-
Top-level = 5
Inner = 3 + 3 = 6
👉 Grand total = 11 entries
